{"tid":434014,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"年終壓軸！NVIDIA GTX 1070 Ti規格定了：月底發佈","createTime":"2017-10-13T01:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T01:31:48.000Z","uid":60286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ad132dd6a3b8eed26e3ffb796f90fcc6fe2dab22","tid":434014,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:31:48.000Z","msg":"在10系顯卡和Volta核心、12nm的20系空檔期，NVIDIA即將推出一款GTX 1070 Ti，達到實現收割AMD RX Vega 56甚至Vega 64潛在消費者的目的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/093009_40fadff2c97458fa2bf85fe3787da111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F093009_40fadff2c97458fa2bf85fe3787da111.jpg&h=f4991f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據TechARP報導，他們拿到了GTX 1070 Ti的一份規格參數表，證實了此前2432個流處理器的傳聞，也就是只比GTX 1080少了一組CU。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/093019_1d97d67fc001a0db97c4e01696009f22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F093019_1d97d67fc001a0db97c4e01696009f22.jpg&h=c5e437a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公版頻率1607-1683MHz，搭配8GB GDDR5顯存，功耗約180W。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/093036_462f9df64983c6d0fad29129d3befa4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F093036_462f9df64983c6d0fad29129d3befa4f.jpg&h=3ed7b6d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同時，陰影和像素填充率都高於GTX 1070，接近GTX 1080，不過8GB GDD5的顯存帶寬只有256GB/s，這出神入化的刀法不愧&ldquo;黃&rdquo;家風範。<br />\n<br />\n價格方面，消息稱海外會在429美元，國行預計3000~3500元。<br />\n<br />\n不出意外的話，GTX 1070 Ti會在10月26日的GTC台北大會上發佈，11月2日上市開賣，居然和iPhone X的節奏踩得幾乎一致。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20171012/5/46/2/%E5%B9%B4%E7%B5%82%E5%A3%93%E8%BB%B8NVIDIA-GTX-1070-Ti%E8%A6%8F%E6%A0%BC%E5%AE%9A%E4%BA%86-%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%88-8005484.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20171012%2F5%2F46%2F2%2F%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25A3%2593%25E8%25BB%25B8NVIDIA-GTX-1070-Ti%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25BD%2588-8005484.html&d=OsW8RhCjDOjl8urPPrlWSf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=69115329\" target=\"_blank\">http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20171012/5/46/2/%E5%B9%B4%E7%B5%82%E5%A3%93%E8%BB%B8NVIDIA-GTX-1070-Ti%E8%A6%8F%E6%A0%BC%E5%AE%9A%E4%BA%86-%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%88-8005484.html</a>"}]}